name: Vizualtech
overview: Vizual Tech is a professional Miami web design company, serving clients worldwide. Our Professional Service offerings include: E-Commerce Solutions, Web Design & Development, Flash Web Design, Logo / Identity Design, Mobile Application Development, Credit Card Merchant Setup, UPS & FedEx API Integration, Wordpress Blog Setup and Search Engine Optimization. Since 2003, Vizual Tech has successfully launched over 200 projects. Our professional team of highly skilled individuals is available and eager to ensure your project success. From small sites to mulit year projects.Our team works extremely well together to put all the pieces that make a website function flawlessly for your client base. Our SEO specialists have years of experience optimizing websites for the top search engines. Using a combination of strategies including keyword placement, search engine ranking reports & Google Local placement we strive to get your website a top ranking.
